{
  "texts": [
    "Once the T5 model is trained, it can be used for grammar and spell correction tasks.",
    "Given a text input with errors, the T5 model generates corrected versions by applying its learned grammar rules and language patterns.",
    "The performance of the T5 grammar correction approach can be evaluated using metrics such as precision, recall, and F1-score by comparing the generated corrections against manually annotated reference corrections.",
    "Overall, the T5 grammar correction approach leverages the power of pre-trained transformer models and fine-tuning techniques to effectively correct grammar and spelling errors in text.",
    "It benefits from the comprehensive understanding of language captured during pre-training and the ability to learn from large-scale datasets."
  ]
}